  "title": "Torque Exerted on Meterstick",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH978175.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a diagram a system made of string, a cradle, a meterstick, and 2 objects. A horizontal meterstick sits in the cradle, which is suspended from the ceiling by a string. The cradle is in the center of the meterstick. A 1.0 kilogram object is suspended from the meterstick 0.25 meter to the left of the center of the cradle. A 0.5 kilogram object is suspended from the right end of the meterstick 0.5 meter to the right of the cradle.\" height=\"415\" src=\"/images/8754d48c1786a9ed3ef0a238d458987e.png\" width=\"450\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Consider the situation shown above in which the center of the meterstick is aligned with the center of the cradle, which is at a position of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x equals 0 meters\"><math alttext=\"x equals 0 meters\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.3em\"></mspace><mtext>m</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. Which of the following statements is correct about the torques exerted on the meterstick?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The torque exerted by the force due to gravity is the greatest torque exerted on the meterstick.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The torque exerted by the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.0 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"1.0 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1.0</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.3em\"></mspace><mtext>kg</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> object is the greatest torque exerted on the meterstick.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The torque exerted by the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.5 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"0.5 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.3em\"></mspace><mtext>kg</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> object is the greatest torque exerted on the meterstick.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The torque exerted by the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.0 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"1.0 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1.0</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.3em\"></mspace><mtext>kg</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> object is equal to the torque exerted by the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.5 kilogram\"><math alttext=\"0.5 kilogram\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.3em\"></mspace><mtext>kg</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> object.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
  },
